OL,12,GMinecraft servers have always been
OL,13,Gdecentralised, but in 2022 Mojang
OL,14,Gattempted to roll out a chat reporting
OL,15,Gsystem. Without the ability to trust
OL,16,Geither the client or the server, this
OL,17,Gturned out to be very difficult to get
OL,18,Gright. Over the next 6 months, we were
OL,19,Gin a cycle of Mojang releasing an
OL,20,Gupdate, and us dropping an exploit. In
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
